headline.main: The Progress in Libya; British Work to Destroy Rommel's Tanks Major Factor in Campaign

lead_paragraph: SPARTANBURG, S.C., Nov. 23 -- The news from North Africa read against the background of both British and Axis communiques, makes it clear that the British have won important initial victories in Libya -- victories that may prove to be decisive, but, from what is known, are not yet so.
abstract: H W Baldwin on Brit progress in Libya
